<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Posts on Ananhu home page</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on Ananhu home page</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.145.0</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 19 Apr 2025 18:23:00 +0530</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to setup a free website using Hugo and GitHub pages</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/hugo/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Apr 2025 18:23:00 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/hugo/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="install-hugo">Install hugo&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>apt install hugo&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="create-a-new-hugo-site-cmd">Create a New Hugo Site CMD&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>hugo new site your-site-name&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="initialize-git-repo">Initialize Git Repo&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>git init&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="add-a-theme-or-submodule">Add a Theme or submodule&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>git submodule add &amp;ndash;depth=1 &lt;a href="https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod.git">https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod.git&lt;/a> themes/PaperMod&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="add-the-theme-to-your-configtoml">Add the theme to your config.toml&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>theme = &amp;ldquo;add your theme name&amp;rdquo;&amp;gt;
theme = &amp;ldquo;PaperMod&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="create-github-repository">Create GitHub Repository&lt;/h1>
&lt;h1 id="connect-local-repository-to-github">Connect Local Repository to GitHub&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>git remote add origin &lt;a href="https://github.com/username/username.github.io.git">https://github.com/username/username.github.io.git&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="configure-hugo-for-github-pages--edit-your-configtoml-file">Configure hugo for GitHub pages : Edit your config.toml file&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>baseURL = &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="https://username.github.io/%22">https://username.github.io/&amp;quot;&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>8: commit and push</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp8/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:54 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp8/</guid><description/></item><item><title>7: create a workflow for github actions</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:46 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp7/</guid><description/></item><item><title>6: configure hugo for github pages</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp6/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:41 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp6/</guid><description/></item><item><title>5: create a repo</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp5/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:37 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp5/</guid><description/></item><item><title>4: add a theme or submodule</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp4/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:32 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp4/</guid><description/></item><item><title>3: initialize github repo</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp3/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:24 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp3/</guid><description/></item><item><title>2: create hugo site CMD</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp2/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:19 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp2/</guid><description>&lt;p>hugo new site your website name&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>1: install hugo</title><link>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp1/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 22:53:14 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://kisip.github.io/anandhu.me/posts/setp1/</guid><description>&lt;p>check your version&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>